{
  "texts": [
    "To make AI learning accessible within these contexts, AI pedagogy must be adapted to non-technical classrooms, and be designed with educators from diverse classrooms.",
    "We situate the current work in the context of art classrooms, where we integrate AI learning materials and tools in art learning.",
    "We exploit multiple ways of knowing about technology -epistemological pluralism -as a framework to understand art making as a way to learn with and about AI.",
    "In this work, we co-designed AI and Art learning materials and tools with 21 creative educators in four languages.",
    "Teachers gained foundational AI knowledge, practical experience with AI tools, and AI prototyping skills."
  ]
}